error: possible out-of-bounds buffer access
   |
 9 |     int pos = bpf_strstr(req, "GET ");
   |               ---------- the value comes from here and is never narrowed
10 |     return req[pos];
   |                ^^^ index can be [INT32_MIN, INT32_MAX], and is never narrowed to the buffer
   |
help: narrow it before indexing, e.g. `if (i < 0 || i >= sizeof(buf)) return 0;`